1-1.Title: *JCNC Yearly Membership Renewal*
1-1.Description: JCNC yearly membership resets today. So, if you had got yearly membership, or would like to get a new yearly (or lifetime) membership, you could obtain it now at http://www.jcnc.org/Membership.

7-16.Title: *Is it my birthday or anniversary?*
7-16.Description: I officially came into this world - the DJSangh telegram app group on this day of 2018.
